Package com.tradingcards.elements.collection

Class CollectionModel

java.lang.Object
com.tradingcards.elements.collection.CollectionModel
public class CollectionModel extends Object
The CollectionModel class manages a user's trading card collection, including individual cards, binders, and decks.

It provides methods to add, retrieve, and remove elements from each type of collection.

      public void removeBinderCollection(String name)
      Removes a binder from the binder collection by its name.

      If the binder is found and successfully removed, a confirmation message is printed. Otherwise, a message indicating the binder was not found is displayed.

      Parameters:
      name - the name of the binder to be removed

      public void removeDeckCollection(String name)
